author: Jeff Parsons
title: First iPhone 6s delivered three days before rest of the world gets it - and owner shares everything
text:
Watch this video again Watch Next 
Apple fans the world over have to wait until Friday, September 25 to get their hands on the iPhone 6s or iPhone 6s Plus . 
Well, apart from one San Diego-based visual designer. 
Adrienne Alpern has mysteriously received her brand new iPhone 6s in the post three days ahead of schedule. 
And she wasted no time in spilling the details of her new gadget slab on Twitter. Not sure how this happened but my #iphone6s arrived early @ATT @apple pic.twitter.com/0hK1BETycl
